Modules/CRUD.title: CRUD
Modules/CRUD.description: CRUD component can be used to create a Rest API. By default this will have a sample book API, it consists of Lambdas, Apigateway DynamodbTables and IAM role with fine-grained access to required resources. API specifications are defined in swagger.

Modules/Email Auth Module.description: Email auth Module can be used to set email authentication using Cognito. This module helps in creating login using email authentication.
